[[Dumba]] (Pyramid)- iri shoko rinotoredzera kubva pachiumbwa chinoonekwa kana tichitema mashanga echigabe nokuamisa kuita matumba. Tiri muchidzidzo Kupimanzimbo kune marudzi ematumba anodanwa zvakasiyana zvichienderana nechiumbwa chiri pahwaro hwedumba racho. Sokuti kune: [[dumba regonyanhanhatu]] (hexagonal pyramid); kwoita [[dumba retsazano]] (square based pyramid); [[dumba regonyanhatu]] (triangular pyramid); [[dumba regonyaina mufanamakonya]] (rectangular pyramid), zvichingodaro.
